Apply comprehensive CSS formatting for:

Typography (font-size, weight, spacing, line-height)

Colors, gradients, shadows, rounding

Layout spacing (padding, margins, gaps)

Borders and separators

Interactive hover/focus effects

Grid/Flexbox responsive layouts

Ensure all components look modern, clean, and professional.

Filtering & Categorization

Include optional elements such as:

Search bars

Dropdown filters

Tag systems

Sort controls

