Accordions

Tabs

Modals

Hover reveals

Toggle switches

Tooltips

Visibility Control

Allow sections to be hidden/shown dynamically.

Use classes for toggling (e.g., .hidden, .active) so the page is easily extendable.

Responsiveness

Use responsive CSS rules (flexbox, grid, media queries).

Ensure the layout adapts to all screen sizes.

Clean, Commented Code

